-- MOVES-Teofilo Masera leaves Morgan Stanley to join Reyl Group
-- 
-- Tue Oct 07, 2014 02:16PM EDT
-- None



Oct 7 (Reuters) - Swiss banking company Reyl Group said it appointed Teofilo Masera managing director of its corporate advisory and structuring division in London.

Masera, who has over 20 years of experience in investment banking, joins from Morgan Stanley <MS.N>, Reyl said in a statement.